36,Line 37,"READ MORE ON PAGE  EQUITY IN CARE In partnership with the American Diabetes  Association, we are sponsoring a three-year  program to reduce health inequities by  removing barriers to tools and technology for  diabetes management, regardless of income  level or insurance status.
