37,Line 38,"READ MORE ON PAGE  INCLUSIVITY  IN TRIALS  In 2021, we launched a platform to promote  more inclusive clinical trials — and dedicated  $5 million to scholarships for Historically  Black Colleges and Universities (HBCUs)  and minority nursing associations.
"
38,Line 39,"The goal  is to produce more racially and ethnically  diverse nurses and trialists who, if given the  opportunity, will dramatically impact trials in  the future.
