"
349,Line 350,"We focus on reducing risks of security breaches  by regularly updating our systems and protocols.
"
350,Line 351,"We have evolved our governance approach  to have laser focus on two prominent cyber  categories: enterprise and product cybersecurity.
"
351,Line 352,"Our Enterprise cybersecurity organization is  focused on ensuring the security and availability  of the systems and technologies that support  Abbott’s business operations.
"
352,Line 353,"There are also  regional cybersecurity leaders deployed in  strategic geographies around the world for local  support.
"
353,Line 354,"This organization is led by Abbott’s  Chief Information Security Officer (CISO).
"
