509,Line 510,"A Stake in Abbott7  Helping employees build an ownership stake  in Abbott is key to our philosophy.
"
510,Line 511,"Several  programs facilitate this:  • • Global long-term incentive program:  grants restricted stock units (RSUs) to  employees, generally beginning at the  manager level.
