588,Line 589,"While social distancing, wearing a mask,  frequent hand washing, and asking that  employees stay home (with pay) if they feel  ill or show symptoms are all critical steps to  maintaining a healthy work environment, our  program of regular testing gave our employees  additional peace of mind as they returned to  the office.
