606,Line 607,"OUR MANAGEMENT APPROACH  Environmental governance and management  fall under our Environment, Health and  Safety (EHS) approach, led by our Board  of Directors and senior management.
"
607,Line 608,"Our  EHS organization reports to the Senior Vice  President, Quality Assurance, Regulatory and  Engineering Services who, in turn, reports to  our Chief Executive Officer (CEO).
"
608,Line 609,"The Senior  Vice President is also the executive sponsor  for the development of our climate and  water strategy.
