609,Line 610,"Policies and Management Systems  Our policies and standards are updated regularly  to reflect best practices, regulatory trends and  requirements.
"
610,Line 611,"A comprehensive audit program  monitors compliance and identifies potential  risks to our business and employees.
"
611,Line 612,"We evaluate EHS risk factors for each site  annually, using insights to determine audit  frequency.
