689,Line 690,"OUR MANAGEMENT APPROACH  Our Water Footprint We perform an annual mapping process to  understand where the water we use comes  from, how it is treated and discharged, and the  impacts our operations have on local basins.
"
690,Line 691,"Most of our sites discharge water to municipal  treatment plants before release to the  environment.
"
691,Line 692,"Those that treat water on-site  and discharge it directly to the environment  are required to meet relevant local regulations.
"
692,Line 693,"Where possible, we reduce withdrawals by  recycling and reusing water.
"
693,Line 694,"Since 2017 , we  have measured how much water is recycled  on-site14 and how it is recycled or reused.
"
