"
839,Line 840,"Responding to  regulations on them is key to our  product stewardship program and  impacts how our products can be  used, recycled and disposed of.
"
840,Line 841,"We  ensure the marketing and sale of  our products comply with current  regulations, not just those in place at  the time of product development.
"
841,Line 842,"Conflict minerals include tantalum,  tin, tungsten and gold — also known as  3TG minerals.
