"
1090,Line 1091,"As such, a cross- functional team — including corporate and  divisional EHS, Procurement and Supply  Chain functions — has partnered to identify  our most carbon-intensive suppliers and  sourcing categories with the greatest  opportunities for emission reductions.
"
