1094,Line 1095,"Addressing Supply Chain Water Risks  By 2030, we aim to work with 50 key suppliers  in high water-stressed areas to reduce risks  to water quality and quantity.
"
1095,Line 1096,"In 2021, we  conducted a water risk assessment to identify  key suppliers.
"
1096,Line 1097,"Using the World Resources  Institute (WRI) AqueductTM Global Water Tool,  this assessment considered supplier industries,  sourcing locations and level of water stress.
"
1097,Line 1098,"Of those identified, 26 suppliers representing  4% of total 2021 spend were engaged through  our Supplier Sustainability Survey to better  understand existing water risk mitigation  efforts and opportunities.
"
