1129,Line 1130,"Cutting the Distance Between  Abbott and Our Suppliers  For many years, our facility in  the Netherlands has relied on a  Germany-based bottle supplier.
"
1130,Line 1131,"However, when a packaging supplier  built a new state-of-the-art  manufacturing factory close to our  own manufacturing facility in 2020,  we took the initiative to source  packaging more locally.
"
1131,Line 1132,"Not only has this switch reduced  manufacturing lead times; it has  drastically cut shipping distances by  217 miles for each shipment — annual  savings of 528,000 miles.
"
1132,Line 1133,"This, in  turn, translates into emission savings  of roughly 754 metric tons of CO 2e  and brings us another step closer to  achieving our emission goals.
"
