2002,Line 2003,"Energy Efficiency To reduce energy demand, we have made several energy-efficient improvements  as retrofits to existing equipment or through active in-house energy management.
"
2003,Line 2004,"Several sites use energy data and innovative methods to identify and quantify  energy inefficiencies in manufacturing processes, often employing external experts.
"
2004,Line 2005,"These insights then inform a list of priority energy demand reduction projects  across the global business.
"
2005,Line 2006,"For example, in Indonesia, many of our motors have  been upgraded with variable speed drives, reducing energy requirements while  retaining performance.
"
2006,Line 2007,"Renewable Energy  We are committed to purchasing a greater proportion of electricity from renewable  sources and are developing a Renewable Energy Procurement initiative to drive  continuous improvement in this area.
"
2007,Line 2008,"In 2021, we purchased 190 million kWh of  low-carbon and renewable energy, resulting in savings of 80,000 metric tons of  CO2e.
"
2008,Line 2009,"In addition, we also generated 1.8 million kWh from solar installations at eight  of our sites.
